beforeMessages.title: Updates are here!

beforeMessages.body:
2023 has been such a busy and joyful year for us. Bryce started walking, and he's all over the place! Dave left his job and is now an independent game designer. And Marissa is settling into her new teaching job.

We feel so blessed, and we wish you all the best over the holidays and for the coming year!
beforeMessages.title: Merry Christmas!
